Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 二吨 看着卡车\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hey, Two Ton, watch the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可不希望我们偷来的钱被偷了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We wouldn't want somebody to steal our stolen money.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 这里禁止停车\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hey, this is a no-parking zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的罚单\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Here's your ticket,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的罚款\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}and here's your fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 米奇\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Nice work, Mikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.31,0:00:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,咳 忍者的基本操作而已\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Eh, it's a ninja thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 咱们把拉斐救出来\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Now let's get Raph out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 没人用经典的老式挂锁了吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Man, whatever happened to good old-fashioned padlocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 那还有什么挑战性呢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Heh. Where's the fun in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这个交给我了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This one's all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.69,0:01:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么 拉斐尔\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What's that, Raphael?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你得大声点 老兄\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You're gonna have to speak up, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我听不见\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 这我听到了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Okay, I heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我正试着工作呢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm trying to work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:01:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 拉夫\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hey, Raph.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 兄弟\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Welcome back, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个暴脾气\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What a hothead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷 嗷 嗷 嗷 嗷 嗷 嗷!\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Ow! Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 拉夫\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Uh, Raph?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间胡闹了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}And why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这里不止有我们\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Because we're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这些怪胎\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Look at the freaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,穿的什么蠢服装\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What's with the dweeby costumes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是万圣节\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This ain't Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你们完蛋了 怪胎\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You're going down, freaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没人敢招惹紫龙帮\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Nobody messes with The Purple Dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是穿着龟服的蠢货\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}especially wearing stupid turtle costumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们快离开这里\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Let's get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,快走 快走 快走\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,给我点绿色\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Gimme some green!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 这比预想的要简单\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Well, that was easier than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,希望再多来几个这样的家伙\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I hope there are more of those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我才刚热了个身呢\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm just getting warmed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 好吧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Uh, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你如愿以偿了 拉斐小子\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}looks like you got your wish, Raphie boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那些家伙是忍者吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Are those guys ninjas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 他们确实有忍者风范\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Well, they're certainly ninja-esque.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,做好应对一切的准备\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Be ready for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定会很享受这个的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I am so gonna enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不错的龙踢腿\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Nice dragon kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 漂亮的凤凰拳\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Ah, sweet double phoenix punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 知道这招吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hey, you know this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,多尼 是我们在打他们\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Don, are we beating them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,还是他们在打我们\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}or are they beating us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们赢的时候再来问我 米奇\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Ask me again when we're winning, Mikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 和我想的一样\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Yeah, that's what I thought.
